def test_data_files(self, tmpdir):
        fake_env(
            tmpdir,
            '[options.data_files]\n'
            'cfg =\n'
            '      a/b.conf\n'
            '      c/d.conf\n'
            'data = e/f.dat, g/h.dat\n',
        )

        with get_dist(tmpdir) as dist:
            expected = [
                ('cfg', ['a/b.conf', 'c/d.conf']),
                ('data', ['e/f.dat', 'g/h.dat']),
            ]
            assert sorted(dist.data_files) == sorted(expected)
